title: Mermaid Chart Catalog
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Mermaid renders plain text into diagrams. This wiki uses [[mermaid-tw5|$:/plugins/orange/mermaid-tw5]], a plugin built on [[Mermaid 11.14.0|https://mermaid.js.org]]. Twenty diagram types are available — nine of them (marked ''New'') require Mermaid 10+ and were not in the original plugin.

---

!! Flows and Processes

|!Diagram|!Best for|
|[[Flowchart]]|Algorithms, workflows, decision trees|
|[[sequenceDiagram 1\|sequenceDiagram 1]]|API interactions, protocol flows, actor communication|
|[[User Journey Diagram]]|UX flows, customer experience mapping|

!! Data and Metrics

|!Diagram|!Best for|
|[[Pie chart diagrams]]|Proportional data at a glance|
|[[XY Chart]] ''New''|Bar and line charts with numeric axes|
|[[Quadrant Chart]] ''New''|2×2 prioritization and positioning matrices|
|[[Sankey Diagram]] ''New''|Flow and allocation — where things come from and go|

