!! How to embed a diagram

Three equivalent ways to put a diagram in any tiddler:

''1. Widget:''

```
<$mermaid text='
flowchart LR
    Start --> Process --> End
'></$mermaid>
```

''2. Block (recommended for multi-line diagrams):''

```
$$$text/vnd.tiddlywiki.mermaid
flowchart LR
    Start --> Process --> End
$$$
```

''3. Tiddler type:'' set the tiddler Type field to `text/vnd.tiddlywiki.mermaid` and write only the diagram syntax as the body. Transclude it anywhere with `{{MyDiagramTiddler}}`.

''Themes:'' pass a `theme` attribute — `default`, `base`, `forest`, `dark`, or `neutral`. See [[Theme Showcase]] for a visual comparison.

''Pan & zoom:'' click any rendered diagram to toggle interactive pan & zoom. Click again to exit.

